title: [Yegharren Valley, Trail]
description: The trail is a bit wider here, as if many woodland creatures have traveled it over the years, and it narrows as it winds through a stand of graceful birches to the south.  A faint scent of burning wood wafts through the cool air, and an owl hoots mournfully somewhere in a nearby tree.
